{"tid":381041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一名司機涉濫收車資被捕","createTime":"2017-08-30T15:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T00:44:39.000Z","uid":19552,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a25d717d442b6afea6b7a3045c1cb2098edaa9","tid":381041,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"警方打擊的士濫收車資，下午拘捕一名五十八歲的士司機，他涉嫌「濫收車資」及「沒有展示的士司機證」。警方下午派員喬裝乘客，由尖沙咀廣東道與北京道交界，乘坐的士前往九龍城窩打老道一間酒店，合理車資應該約四十元，但司機收取二百元，警方即時將他拘捕，他獲准保釋候查，十月上旬向警方報到。"},{"pid":"ca7b0c6430df78f8a26ec7436f420cdb55f0b0d0","tid":381041,"uid":3098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88faf3eeff64d7dbc8853809262d0b1c8d0fd901","tid":381041,"uid":33792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:25:07.000Z","msg":"呃正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e0ddec19018631da67582a8e4b1ce3465e1501","tid":381041,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:26:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd4841daa87cbac6267b85d315873b012ad70d3b","tid":381041,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:28:58.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀去九龍城收兩舊又真係大咬左D"},{"pid":"7c6c9cfba4828c7005f295c93b688f063cd4f2bf","tid":381041,"uid":98961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"黃秋生出場未"},{"pid":"7ca8169d06178d3641a895d25c84bb186a25f489","tid":381041,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"喬裝乘客?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4878ccfc460b3247cb7b2eed140daa11125313d7","tid":381041,"uid